Description : - Loading Knowledge Module - Loads data from a JMS compliant Message Oriented Middleware (MOM) to any ISO-92 compliant target database. - This module uses Sunopsis Agent to read selected data from the source MOM and write the result in the target temporary table created dynamically.
Restrictions: - The message format must be either delimited or fixed length. - Each message is a database record.
